        "timestamp": "2020-03-11 18:59:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(3 comments)",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "d8c3076763dd207a14f3c3c6069d3aad50fdb909",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 477,
          "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-03-11 19:03:34.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nNeed some changes in the Dockerfile to remove the amsterdam lines, and can add a line to add \"frankfurt\" one that I missed to comment in Jim's review.\n\nI can do some changes in OOM to remove any amsterdam references.\n\nDo a global search for amsterdam in the repo, I think there are some scripts such as \"create-cl-amsterdam\" that will need to be removed too.\n\nBut let's make sure we are all in agreement with my previous questions.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
